OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly but bright start to
OL,6,Fthe day. Plenty of sunny spells
OL,7,Fthrough the morning and stretching
OL,8,Finto the afternoon. A fresher feeling
OL,9,Fday than of late but winds staying
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FQuickly clouding over this
OL,13,Fevening, with outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fdeveloping by the early hours. Staying
OL,15,Fwet overnight, with the rain heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes over the hills. Turning
OL,17,Fincreasingly blustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
