OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA blustery day, with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, which could be
OL,7,Fheavy at times. A few bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells possible, mainly during the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWindy
OL,12,Fon Saturday, with showers or longer
OL,13,Fspells of rain. Bright and breezy on
OL,14,FEaster Sunday, with a scattering of
OL,15,Fshowers. Drier and warmer for Easter
OL,16,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
